  "datePublished": "2026-03-09",
  "description": "A scenario is the prepared package of situations, locations, non-player characters, pressures, and clues that a [tabletop role-playing game](../index.md) group will engage during play. It is not a script for what the players must do. It is the authored starting state and the actionable parts of the world that the [game master](../../terms/game-master.md) can bring to the table.",
